<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śākābdē ratnanākaddyumaṇipa
<lb n="2" break="no"/>rimitē caitramāsē daśamyāṁ śuklē
<lb n="3" break="no"/>sminsūryyavārē maṇimakuṭayu
<lb n="4" break="no"/>tāṁ kkāṁccanāṁggīṁ bhbhavānīṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> prādādbhīmēśvarā
<lb n="5" break="no"/>yatribhuvanapatayēdharmmadātāṁkkamāṁbā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>mēnādēvīviṣādaṁ śamayatumaniśa
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ṁ matsyavaṁśārjjunēśa<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> <supplied reason="omitted">1</supplied> citrastaṁbhbhacatu
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṣṭayēna vilasatśayyā<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied>tarastaśśivādē
<lb n="9" break="no"/>vī<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied>ratnakirīṭasōbhitavapussavurnnagātrī<unclear>ṁ</unclear>
<lb n="10"/>satīṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> kiṁ grihṇatyadhunā mahēsvarasṛ
<lb n="11" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> tisthitā <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> karttha <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="12"/>sthitā yuvatayastvāṁ ta(kka)rkkayaṁ <unclear>tō</unclear>ṁbikāṁ [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 2*]
<lb n="13"/>svasti <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrīśakavaruṣaṁbulu 1209 gu nēṁṭi
<lb n="14"/>caitra śuddha daśamiyu ravivāramunāṁḍu [O]
<lb n="15" break="no"/>ḍḍanādi matsyakulatilaka Arjjunadēvarāju
<lb n="16" break="no"/>la dēvi dākṣārāmakoṁḍḍikamunnūṁṭiĀṭya
<lb n="17" break="no"/>gaḍiyavaseṭṭivīrapanēni kūṁttuṟu Akkamadēvi
<lb n="18"/>śrīmaddākṣārāmabhīmvēśaramahādēvarakuṁ cai
<lb n="19" break="no"/>tradavanaparvvamiḍōṟōtsavamunāṁṭṭihaviba
<lb n="20" break="no"/>lyādi A<unclear>r</unclear>ccanaku Oḍḍādilōvali maṟuvāḍi Ūru Ā
<lb n="21" break="no"/>caṁdrārkkasthāyigāṁ beṭṭi śrībhīmēśvaramahādēvara
<lb n="22" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> paramēśvariśrīyyaṁggamu pahiṁḍi gaṭṭi<note n="481-2">The inscription stops with this.</note> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> 
